              <li><strong>Address:</strong> 50 Centre St. S., Oshawa, ON L1H 3Z7</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <p>Bylaws can change. The information here reflects Licensing By-law 122-2024 and MAT By-law 93-2020 as amended through 2024, but always check the city's website for the most current version.</p>

